original_title: 歌舞伎町ブラックスワン キャバクラ・風俗・AV 闇の女手配師-深雪-
overview: Aika (Ruka Kanae) has shaken off the persistent scoutman who called out to her in Shinjuku Kabukicho. I thought I was relieved when I ran away, but behind me called out, "Don't you want a job that can earn more money than you do now?" and when I turned around, I saw a beautiful woman there. She was a very successful female scout in Kabukicho, Fukayuki (Ai Sayama).
title: Kabukicho Black Swan
